  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK713">
<l>avaiyaṟiyār collaṉmēṟ koḷpavar colliṉ</l>
<l>vakaiyaṟiyār vallatūu mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who undertake to speak without knowing the (nature of the) court are ignorant of the quality of words as well as devoid of the power (of learning).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
